name: Slide Lock For Showcases
description:
Durable laminate exterior finish with glass front, top and sides. Features melamine laminated surfaces, bright white deck and doors, ships fully assembled, satin finish clear anodized aluminum frame extrusions, matching steel interior standard and brackets, tempered glass top, front, sides, shelves. Two rows of adjustable 1/4" split glass shelves (one row 8" deep, one row 10" deep). Steel standards and brackets. White deck and rear sliding doors. 38"H x 20"D, glass display area is 26"H x 20"D. Base is 12"H, available in 48" and 70" lengths.  The case comes in Gray (very light gray), Black or Maple. Colors of cases may differ from the actual showcases.   
Optional lock and light kit sold separately.

This product will be shipped VIA common carrier. Freight will be quoted separately. You will be notified of the freight amount.
